@startuml
!include ../include/diagram-style.puml

title View Trail Information

actor "End User" as EU
boundary SearchPanel
boundary TrailPanel
control TrailService
database Database

EU -> SearchPanel : select trail, Open

SearchPanel -> TrailPanel : setTrail(trailId) / open detail

TrailPanel -> TrailService : getTrail(trailId)
TrailService -> Database : fetchTrailById(trailId)
Database --> TrailService : trail

note right of TrailService
  Trail already contains wildlifeList
  (joined from catalog when loaded).
end note

TrailService --> TrailPanel : trail

TrailPanel --> EU : display trail metadata,\ntrail images, wildlife text + thumbnails

@enduml
